Text: RE TISVoucher Kickouts Report Please begin reviewing this report for closePlease disregard the following message as it was sent to the wrong Outlook users in error Original Message From Heath Deborah Sent Thursday September PM To DLV Users Subject TISVoucher Kickouts Report Please begin reviewing this report for close The TIS upgrade project has provided the addition of a new report called TISVoucher Kickouts Several kickouts currently exists on this report for the August close Please remember to review this report for MSA accounts and invalid JIA tables that appear for your companies Resolving these errors will help expedite the process for all users For more information on the TISVoucher Kickouts report please visit taxenroncom and click on the Tax Informer TaxInformertinformerasplink There is a section in Tax Informer that discusses changes to the Ad Hoc database including the addition of the TISVoucher Kickouts report For additional questions on this new report please contact Kelly McCain ext or Deborah Heath ext Thanks Tax Solutions Team
